  "body": "Since we can install a chart from a remote repository:\n\n```\n$ ./helm install kubernetes-charts/alpine-0.1.0.tgz\n```\n\nThe question is, how do we know what properties we can set for the chart ? Without downloading it, untarring it and checking the values.yam file.\n\nWe can definitely let helm use the defaults, but for helm to know the values that can be set for a chart it needs a way to introspect the chart, which might mean a round trip with tiller during deployment...\n",
